<paragraph blockId="9.[264,1324,1653,1879]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
REMARKS. 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis" box="[427,628,1653,1679]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. (1993) Catalog of the types of southern African Mythicomyiidae (Insecta: Diptera). Genus, 4, 91 - 102." type="journal article" year="1993">
Evenhuis (
<number box="[558,619,1653,1679]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="1993.0">1993</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
gave information of the 
<typeStatus box="[948,1051,1653,1679]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">holotype</typeStatus>
female in 
<collectionCode box="[1193,1285,1653,1679]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">BMNH</collectionCode>
. A 
<typeStatus box="[264,365,1693,1719]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">paratype</typeStatus>
female in 
<collectionCode box="[496,582,1693,1719]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/94p5-pepz" name="Iziko Museums of Cape Town" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">SAMC</collectionCode>
, topotypic with the 
<typeStatus box="[823,928,1693,1719]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">holotype</typeStatus>
, has also been examined during this study and is, like the 
<typeStatus box="[563,668,1733,1759]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">holotype</typeStatus>
, glued on its side on a yellowing clear plastic stage. No additional material has been found since the original material was collected. The original description and salient characters given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Hesse" box="[783,942,1813,1839]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refString="Hesse, A. J. (1938) Revision of the Bombyliidae of Southern Africa. Annals of the South African Museum, 34, 1 - 1053." type="journal article" year="1938">
Hesse (
<number box="[872,933,1813,1839]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="1938.0">1938</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
serve to adequately distinguish the species.
</paragraph>
